<HEADLINE>
FT  01 FEB 94 / World News in Brief: French novelist Pierre Boulle dies
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
French novelist Pierre Boulle, whose novels Bridge on the River Kwai and
Planet of the Apes were turned into screen blockbusters, has died aged 81,
his publisher said.
</TEXT>
